  * Dark color scheme (color-scheme=prefer-dark, gtk-theme=Adwaita-dark)
  * TMJOs wallpaper as the desktop background
  * JetBrains Mono as the monospace font
  * Disables distro dock/appindicator/desktop-icon extensions when
